.name
Uedit-Stuff
.author
Paul Kienitz 
.description
A variety of configuration material for Uedit.  Includes stuff for
remembering multiple chunks of deleted text, interfacing through Rexx with
a terminal program, displaying matching '(' characters when you press ')',
expanding abbreviations into phrases as you type, easily shifting lines and
blocks of text left or right, improvements to several existing Uedit
features, and more.  
